title: 276. The Skewed Balance Of High Performers
itunes:title: 276. The Skewed Balance Of High Performers
description: In today's episode, Andy explains how soft people have hijacked the term 'balance,' causing a mediocrity epidemic in society, where high achievers focus their efforts to accomplish massive goals and the best way to build the life you want around your mission.
